thread.title: Brandon Worton
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Brandon Worton

author: Brandon Worton
title: Brandon Worton
text: Although you will still be making trips to the store to obtain your favorite baits, you are met with a reliable income of new and diverse baits that can widen the horizons of your fishing ability. Learning to use new baits is something a new or old fisherman can benefit from and everyone who fishes loves to catch fish using new baits. Now if only there were better fishing on my home lake!
